						<h1>愛狗人士小心！蜱蟲咬上眼　女子眼皮刺痛遭殃</h1>

						
						<div id="reporter_info">
														
						<a href="/home/coraline/Documents/Corpus/readability/corpus/zh/html/20120117_member.nownews.com_459ef99970ffd92d262efdc9aded538182e7dd4e2cb6a3cc29cd3882" target="_blank">
